text: Haplolobus inaequifolius is a species of plant in the Burseraceae family. It is a tree endemic to Borneo where it is confined to Sarawak. ==References== inaequifolius Category:Endemic flora of Borneo Category:Trees of Borneo Category:Flora of Sarawak Category:Vulnerable plants Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
